cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SY, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on logical specification and synthesis of shields using formulas of logic Quantified Discrete Duration Calculus (QDDC). 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper deals with run-time enforcement of software controllers. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of a tool for automatic synthesis of shields from a given specification. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controllers and their output. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of quantitative optimization to give a shield which minimizes the expected value of cumulative deviation in an H-optimal fashion.
